cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper deals with unsupervised video prediction using deep learning and physical knowledge described by partial differential equations (PDEs). Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a new recurrent physical cell (PhyCell) for performing PDE-constrained prediction, which could fall under neural networks (cs.NE) or systems and control (cs.SY).
